-- Treasury Sanctions Iran’s Bank Tejarat for ‘Illicit’ Activities
-- B y   I a n   K a t z
-- 2012-01-23T18:19:11Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-01-23/treasury-sanctions-iran-s-bank-tejarat-for-illicit-activities.html
The U.S. Treasury Department
sanctioned  Iran ’s Bank Tejarat for providing financial services
to banks and companies already subject to international
restrictions.  The U.S. has now sanctioned 23 Iranian-linked financial
institutions “based on their involvement in Iran’s illicit
activities,” the Treasury said in a statement in  Washington 
today.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Ian Katz in Washington at 
 ikatz2@bloomberg.net .  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
